*!            pick ticket. 
*! 컴컴컴컴컴컴컴컴컴컴컴컴컴컴컴컴컴컴컴컴컴컴컴컴컴컴컴컴컴
*! Called from : 
*!         Procedures : ALPKTKFC.
*!*************************************************************
PROCEDURE lpOldFoter

@ 55,93 SAY XSTNAME
@ 56,93 SAY XSTADDR1
@ 57,12 SAY '*** CONTINUED NEXT PAGE ***'
